quote_five: Saving today ensures a brighter tomorrow.
quote_four: The habit of saving is itself an education; it fosters every virtue, teaches self-denial, cultivates the sense of order, and trains to forethought.
quote_one: A penny saved is a penny earned.
quote_three: Saving is the gap between your ego and your income.
quote_two: Do not save what is left after spending, but spend what is left after saving.
